cs.LG, cs.IR, cs.DS, cs.MA, cs.AI 

The paper proposes a reinforcement learning framework for budget constrained bidding in online display advertising. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.LG (Machine Learning), followed by cs.IR (Information Retrieval) and cs.DS (Data Structures and Algorithms) as the paper deals with optimization problems and large-scale datasets. The paper also involves decision-making processes, which could fall under cs.MA (Multi-Agent Systems) and cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence).
